&lt;p&gt;We are looking for highly motivated Staff Nurses to join our established, busy 28 bedded Surgical ward at the Conquest Hospital. You will need to have a keen interest in general surgery and be committed to delivering a high standard of patient care, whilst maintaining your own personal professional development. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We will provide a supportive environment and mentorship. We are committed to professional developing our staff. Team working is an integral part of the running of our ward. This is an exciting opportunity for an enthusiastic and motivated nurse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We currently operate 11.5 hour shifts on internal rotation. However, come and see us if you have an interest in Surgery and require specific shifts. We will see if we can help enhance your career whilst offering shifts that fit in with you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information or an informal discussion telephone Jacinta Isles, Ward Matron on 01424 755255&lt;/p&gt;
